			i3-utils

This repository contains severals scripts which extend the
functionality of i3/sway among other tasks for my workflow.

Scripts:

	i3-clam-shell		manage laptop screens
	i3-cycle-focus		emulate 'alt-tab'
	i3-file-picker		dmenu-based file manager
	i3-new-workspace	find next empty workspace
	i3-run-or-raise		focus if open, else launch
	i3-select-theme		personal theme configs
	i3-select-window	focus window with dmenu
	i3-title-status		status info in window title

Dependencies:

	AnyEvent::I3 (https://metacpan.org/pod/AnyEvent::I3)

Installation:

	git clone https://github.com/dhennigar/i3-utils
	cd i3-utils
	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Documentation:

	Each function is documented via POD,
	accessible with `perldoc`.
